name: 2000 little fishes by Eva Cortez
description:
Today we are a great flock of fish in this great NFT ocean.

Today we celebrate belonging to this community! Diverse and supportive.

This character belongs to my collection called "Ellas by Eva Cortez".
Each one of "Ellas" tells a story. 

2D digital animation on offer. 
Animation resolution 1600px x 2250px in GIF format.

Completion date: December 09, 2021 
Technique: Digital drawing and 2D animation 
Software: Medibang Pain Pro and Photoshop.

The artwork may not be reproduced commercially. The author reserves the right to use the image of the work for merchandising.

You will have access to my Discord server. Once there you will have access to the exclusive channel for collectors. 

In this private channel I will share with you the release of new drops. Special gifts. Exclusive access to my creative process.

By supporting the "Ellas by Eva Cortez" Art Project, you are not only promoting an artist, you are promoting Hispanic and female inclusion in the NFT ecosystem. Opening a world of opportunities for these artists. Learn more about this project on my website: 
https://evacortezarte.wixsite.com/website/ellasbyevacortez 

Thank you for supporting my work!
